      <hedline>
        <hl1>Responsible Wheels</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>W Dana Holman letter urges Americans to start driving environmentally and socially responsible vehicles</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''G.M. Has High Hopes for Vehicle Truly Meant for Road Warriors'' (front page, Aug. 6):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''G.M. Has High Hopes for Vehicle Truly Meant for Road Warriors'' (front page, Aug. 6):</p>
        <p>You quote the father of a 9-year-old girl as looking forward to buying a Hummer for her when she turns 16. The only way his daughter, and all our children, will have air they can breathe in the future is if Americans start driving environmentally and socially responsible vehicles.</p>
        <p>W. DANA HOLMAN  Astoria, Queens, Aug. 9, 2000</p>
      </block>
    </body.content>
